an/Getty Images for LACMA）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-XCX-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-XCX-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-XCX-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-XCX-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-XCX-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-XCX-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>在她正在进行的“Brat”世界巡演中离开了伦敦，她带来了朋友<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robyn">Robyn</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caroline-polachek">Caroline Polachek</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yung-lean">Yung Lean</a> 。查看下面的照片、片段和歌单。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-and-its-completely-different-but-also-still-brat-review-a-masterpiece-in-the-art-of-club-music-curatorship-3802412">Charli XCX – “Brat And It’s Completely Different but Also Still Brat”评论：俱乐部音乐策展艺术的杰作</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">“Brat”夏季文化现象的影响下，</a>查莉在英国旋风般的一年中取得了胜利，受到她<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">广受好评的第六张专辑</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-and-its-completely-different-but-also-still-brat-review-a-masterpiece-in-the-art-of-club-music-curatorship-3802412">随后的混音唱片</a>的启发，查理<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-brat-uk-tour-manchester-so-i-remix-sophie-george-daniel-photos-setlist-video-3816842">昨天在曼彻斯特的 Co-Op Live 拉开序幕</a>后，在伦敦的 O2 体育场进行了表演，她在那里首次推出了《So I》的混音版，以向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sophie">SOPHIE</a>致敬。</p><p>昨晚（11 月 28 日），Charli 大部分表演了她<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">大获成功的第六张专辑</a>及其<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-and-its-completely-different-but-also-still-brat-review-a-masterpiece-in-the-art-of-club-music-curatorship-3802412">混音版</a>中的曲目，包括《Club classics》、开场曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shygirl">《Shygirl</a> 》的《365》以及《Apple》，后者是一场以观众为主角的音乐会主打歌曲。表演火爆的 TikTok 舞蹈。这一次，查理的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-reveals-talk-talk-is-about-nearly-following-the-1975s-george-daniel-to-the-toilet-at-the-nme-awards-3764123">未婚夫、1975 年的乔治·丹尼尔</a>尝试了这一尝试。</p><p>节目第三部分结束后，扩音器播放了由波拉切克 (Polachek) 主演的《一切都是浪漫》的混音版，随后由《欲望，我想变成你》艺术家查理 (Charli) 进行了独奏表演，而《欲望，我想变成你》艺术家则出现在安可表演中。使混音版首次现场亮相。之后，查理和波拉切克表演了后者的“欢迎来到我的岛”的版本，由丹尼尔重新混音。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Charli XCX 在伦敦 O2 现场表演“Apple”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Rp3YNrEeonU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Charli XCX、Caroline Polachek - Everything is Romantic Remix (Live @ Brat Tour London O2 Arena)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_U4hn49P2pk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DC7x7rciJ2n/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; paddin